{"type":"message","id":"cb9f1def","parentId":"dd5620c6","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:08:24.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md and related context to see if anything needs attention.\n\nCurrent time: Saturday, March 28th, 2026 — 4:08 AM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nKey checks:\n1. Is it a trading day? Saturday - no\n2. Scheduled work:\n   - Workspace backup: daily\n   - Quant ops: trading days only (not today - Saturday)\n   - Self-improvement: daily afternoon/evening (4 AM is too early)\n\nLet me check if there are active tasks, checklists, or anything that needs attention.","thinkingSignature":"a41fbc68dbb45d45517a469c2b3f754705529488610d2efe2c3042684a063e7a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_14n05aex5fyf_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_14n05aex5fyf_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK*.md 2>/dev/null && cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK*.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"NO_ACTIVE_TASK\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66,"output":227,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":23249,"totalTokens":23542,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774642097180,"responseId":"061616b1809999d6ca5bed9bd53a2bab"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f0d0844","parentId":"cb9f1def","timestamp":"2026-03-27T20:08:24.436Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_14n05aex5fyf_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774642104424}}
