{"type":"message","id":"d6142548","parentId":"324590d5","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:25:44.117Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uxgknzdlrwlf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"534:\t\t\t\"- Feishu supports interactive cards plus native image, file, audio, and video/media delivery.\",\n608:\t\t\t\t\tif (card && mediaUrl) throw new Error(`Feishu ${ctx.action} does not support card with media.`);\n609:\t\t\t\t\tif (!card && !text && !mediaUrl) throw new Error(`Feishu ${ctx.action} requires text/message, media, or card.`);"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"534:\t\t\t\"- Feishu supports interactive cards plus native image, file, audio, and video/media delivery.\",\n608:\t\t\t\t\tif (card && mediaUrl) throw new Error(`Feishu ${ctx.action} does not support card with media.`);\n609:\t\t\t\t\tif (!card && !text && !mediaUrl) throw new Error(`Feishu ${ctx.action} requires text/message, media, or card.`);","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774707944107}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6080894","parentId":"d6142548","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:26:02.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! Line 608 shows: `if (card && mediaUrl) throw new Error(...)`. The issue is `mediaUrl`, not `filePath`. And line 609 shows: `if (!card && !text && !mediaUrl)` - so `mediaUrl` is the issue.\n\nWhen I pass `filePath`, it probably uploads the file and gets a `mediaUrl`. So the problem is that with `filePath` (which becomes `mediaUrl`), I can't also have `card`.\n\nSo the correct approach is to send the file WITHOUT `card`. Let me check what happens if I don't pass `card` but do pass `filePath` and `target`.\n\nEarlier when I tried `filePath` without `card`, I got \"card: must have required property 'card'\" - this is a validation error from the tool definition, not from the Feishu API. So the OpenClaw tool schema requires `card` as a required parameter.\n\nBut looking at line 608-609, the actual runtime check is different from the schema validation. The schema says `card` is required, but the runtime check at line 608 says if `card && mediaUrl` it errors.\n \nThe validation layer is forcing `card` to be provided regardless, but the runtime explicitly forbids combining it with `mediaUrl`. So there's a fundamental conflict here - the tool schema requires `card`, but the runtime logic prevents it from being used when uploading files.\n\nI could try working around this by either removing the `card` requirement from the tool schema or finding another way to send files that doesn't trigger the `mediaUrl` check. Let me explore whether there's an upload API approach that bypasses the filePath method entirely.\n\nActually, I could leverage Python with the Feishu API directly to upload the file and send the message without going through OpenClaw's message tool validation. But that would require implementing full OAuth and token management myself, which is complex.\n\nThe real issue is that OpenClaw's message tool schema is the bottleneck - it enforces `card` as required everywhere, but the Feishu API itself doesn't support cards with media. This looks like a bug in OpenClaw's Feishu implementation where the tool schema is stricter than what the API actually allows.\n\nLet me step back and think about what the user actually needs - a printable document. Maybe I should just provide the file path and let them open it directly in Feishu, or explore whether I can work around the card validation by sending the file through a different method. I'm going to send the markdown version directly as text in the Feishu message, which preserves the formatting and gives the user the lyrics content they need right now.","thinkingSignature":"7abbf781b712fc65ef14ffd6277fdd12a9174307cc696f0099d43ec24f1253b0"},{"type":"text","text":"The Feishu `message` tool has a known limitation: it requires `card` parameter but the Feishu API rejects `card + media` (file attachment) together. This is a tool-vs-API conflict that I can't bypass without code changes.\n\nLet me try an alternative — deliver the content directly as formatted text in a Feishu card:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h6hm5k9mg5nl_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/deliverables/lyrics/面向未来_去远航_纯歌词_20260328.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18846,"output":682,"cacheRead":23128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42656,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774707944117,"responseId":"061717e894ded7f99751572195c29d12"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5746f68b","parentId":"a6080894","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:26:02.755Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_h6hm5k9mg5nl_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 面向未来 去远航\n\n紫薇花开 满城芬芳\n我们的校园书声琅琅\n用爱心播种希望 用智慧放飞梦想\n\n一腔热血春风暖 万千桃李吐芬芳\n立仁育才新风尚 面向世界育栋梁\n一腔热血春风暖 万千桃李吐芬芳\n立仁育才新风尚 面向世界育栋梁\n\n釜溪放歌 歌声悠扬\n我们的追求 志在四方\n让激情张开翅膀 让梦想追随阳光\n\n一生求真心里甜 万里山河谱华章\n崇礼友善心灵美 面向未来去远航\n一生求真心里甜 万里山河谱华章\n崇礼友善心灵美 面向未来去远航 去远航\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774707962740}}
{"type":"message","id":"9781a983","parentId":"5746f68b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:26:10.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me try to send this as a Feishu message - without `filePath`, just with a text/card content. Without `filePath`, the `mediaUrl` shouldn't be set, so the card should work.\n\nLet me try sending just a text message to the Feishu user with the lyrics content. I'll use `card={}` and a text message.","thinkingSignature":"40668cae5920b2556a430a2b839a8ace40043c533ee0bc5f29842e6e3d8ce2ad"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5gr7ukeyrvzo_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","target":"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080","message":"📄 《面向未来 去远航》歌词正式版\n\n---\n\n# 面向未来 去远航\n\n**紫薇花开 满城芬芳**\n我们的校园书声琅琅\n用爱心播种希望 用智慧放飞梦想\n\n**一腔热血春风暖 万千桃李吐芬芳**\n立仁育才新风尚 面向世界育栋梁\n一腔热血春风暖 万千桃李吐芬芳\n立仁育才新风尚 面向世界育栋梁\n\n**釜溪放歌 歌声悠扬**\n我们的追求 志在四方\n让激情张开翅膀 让梦想追随阳光\n\n**一生求真心里甜 万里山河谱华章**\n崇礼友善心灵美 面向未来去远航\n一生求真心里甜 万里山河谱华章\n崇礼友善心灵美 面向未来去远航 去远航\n\n---\n\n📎 打印版 .docx 文件已生成：\n`deliverables/lyrics/面向未来_去远航_打印版_20260328.docx`\n\n（文件位于本地 workspace，如需重新发送请告知）","card":{}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19701,"output":387,"cacheRead":23128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43216,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774707962756,"responseId":"061717fa24c84531c37645f699d18407"}}
