{"type":"message","id":"9a86b36e","parentId":"aad9d124","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:26:55.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the flow:\n1. `card` is parsed from `ctx.params.card` - if it's an object, it's used as the card content\n2. `text` is read from `ctx.params.text` or `ctx.params.message`\n3. `mediaUrl` comes from `readFeishuMediaParam(ctx.params)`\n\nThe issue is:\n- When I provide `card={}`, it's treated as a card object, so `card` is truthy\n- Without `filePath`, `mediaUrl` should be empty\n- So it goes to `runtime.sendCardFeishu()` which is probably failing because `{}` is an empty card\n\nThe 400 error when sending an empty card `{}` suggests that Feishu's API rejects empty cards.\n\n\nI should try passing a properly structured Feishu interactive card with actual content instead of an empty object, since Feishu supports interactive cards as a native message type. Let me look at the Feishu card documentation to construct a valid format.\n\nActually, I'm realizing the core issue: the `message` tool in this channel has `card` marked as required in the schema, but Feishu's API itself doesn't accept cards with file attachments, and empty cards get rejected too. This looks like a limitation in OpenClaw's implementation rather than something I can work around. I think the best path forward is to acknowledge this to the user and offer concrete alternatives, or try constructing a minimal but valid Feishu card with actual content.\n\nLet me attempt one more approach: a properly formatted Feishu card with a note element containing the lyrics text and a mention that the docx file is attached. If that still fails, I'll just inform the user that the Feishu file delivery has a technical blocker and provide the direct file path instead.","thinkingSignature":"8231b56f9195356a01770bd4bc6cd32111e509ec9c5bd94ccf8ec1c77869db18"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oaynwxlqaa88_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","target":"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080","message":"📄 《面向未来 去远航》歌词已整理完成\n\n一、紫薇花开 满城芬芳 / 我们的校园书声琅琅 / 用爱心播种希望 用智慧放飞梦想\n\n二、一腔热血春风暖 万千桃李吐芬芳 / 立仁育才新风尚 面向世界育栋梁\n\n三、釜溪放歌 歌声悠扬 / 我们的追求 志在四方 / 让激情张开翅膀 让梦想追随阳光\n\n四、一生求真心里甜 万里山河谱华章 / 崇礼友善心灵美 面向未来去远航\n\n📎 打印版 docx 文件已生成，路径：\ndeliverables/lyrics/面向未来_去远航_打印版_20260328.docx\n\n（飞书文件直发通道暂因工具兼容性问题不可用，请通过 workspace 访问文件）","card":{"type":"app","body":{"type":"markdown","content":"📄 **《面向未来 去远航》歌词已整理完成**\n\n一、紫薇花开 满城芬芳 / 我们的校园书声琅琅 / 用爱心播种希望 用智慧放飞梦想\n\n二、一腔热血春风暖 万千桃李吐芬芳 / 立仁育才新风尚 面向世界育栋梁\n\n三、釜溪放歌 歌声悠扬 / 我们的追求 志在四方 / 让激情张开翅膀 让梦想追随阳光\n\n四、一生求真心里甜 万里山河谱华章 / 崇礼友善心灵美 面向未来去远航\n\n📎 打印版 docx：`deliverables/lyrics/面向未来_去远航_打印版_20260328.docx`"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22370,"output":813,"cacheRead":23128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46311,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774707991313,"responseId":"06171817cea94dbf0f39fef35b7ca656"}}
